# Gamma Concentration
# 40Hz focus for analytical work
# Use when: Debugging, problem-solving, deep analysis

# Ground first
safety(grounding: 7.5)

# Ramp up to focus state
optimize(for: :focus, level: 0.7)

# Driving rhythm for sustained attention
kick(every: 4) + snare(every: 8, offset: 4) + hihat(times: 16)

# Maintain focus
# Sharp, clear, precise
